Package: pharmax.ml
Title: R-Native Machine Learning Helpers for Pharmacometrics
Version: 0.3.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Malek", "Okour", , "malek@zajaly.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Malek Okour
Maintainer: Malek Okour <malek@zajaly.com>
Description: R-native machine learning helpers for exploratory pharmacometric
    workflows. Includes covariate screening, conformal prediction intervals,
    explainability helpers, data quality checks, ensemble summaries, synthetic
    benchmarks, calibration summaries, and bounded evidence summaries.
